      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CRIS TESSA (2) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 2 lengths at Sandown in a handy 29.58 beating Tony. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Great chance again. FEIKUAI CALVIN (3) has been in the placings at his last two runs, most recently when third (24.62) in a Grade 5 H over 435m at Sale. Well placed here and can atone this time. CANYA ADIRA (7) was prominent throughout when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when 4th and beaten 6 lengths at Sandown (29.81). The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. A big run wouldn't surprise. NANGAR CHARM (6) warrants respect although new to this track.",
